---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/sections/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Heading from '../components/ui/Heading.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services | Geek Life Development"
  description="Explore website builds, simple web apps, and ongoing support designed for clear scope, practical delivery, and steady growth."
>
  <Hero
    title="Services designed to ship modern digital work without the chaos"
    subtitle="Built for small businesses in Cedarburg and Milwaukee, plus remote creators and startups who need clear scope, clean execution, and steady momentum."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Get a quote', href: '/contact' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'See pricing', href: '/pricing' }}
    accent={false}
  />

  <Section>
    <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Websites"
        title="Our main offering: modern websites with subscription-friendly support"
        subtitle="We build responsive sites that look polished, load fast, and give you an SEO-ready foundation from day one."
      />

      <Card hover={false}>
        <p class="label-mono text-slate-500">Typical website engagement includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li>• Messaging-led page structure and conversion-focused flow</li>
          <li>• Responsive implementation across mobile, tablet, and desktop</li>
          <li>• SEO-friendly technical setup and clean content architecture</li>
          <li>• Ongoing subscription-based support for updates and improvements</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-4xl space-y-4">
      <p>
        This is ideal for businesses that want a strong web presence without rebuilding from scratch every few months.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Not enterprise-scale custom platforms.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="muted">
    <div class="space-y-10">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Simple apps"
        title="Simple apps that solve one core problem well"
        subtitle="When a website isn’t enough, we build lean product layers to handle specific workflows without unnecessary complexity."
      />

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Member portals (lightweight)</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Access-controlled pages for members, clients, or internal teams.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Simple reporting views that surface the numbers your team actually uses.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Scheduling systems</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Booking and availability flows designed for smoother operations.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Internal tools</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Small utility apps that remove repetitive manual work.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Form-driven workflows</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Structured submissions, triage logic, and cleaner handoffs.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <p>Everything is built lean, with scope focused on the most important workflow first.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Not full SaaS platforms.</p>
        <Button href="/contact">Discuss your idea</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Ongoing support"
        title="Support and maintenance that keeps momentum"
        subtitle="After launch, we continue with monthly updates and focused improvements so your digital presence keeps up with your business."
      />

      <Card hover={false}>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li>• Monthly updates and quality checks</li>
          <li>• Iterative UX and content improvements</li>
          <li>• Hosting guidance and deployment support</li>
          <li>• Performance and security basics handled consistently</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      A subscription model works better than one-off rebuilds because progress compounds over time instead of restarting each quarter.
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="muted">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Boundaries"
        title="What we don’t do"
        subtitle="Clear boundaries help keep projects honest, healthy, and successful."
      />
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No bloated builds</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No mystery retainers</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No long-term lock-ins</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No cheap and rushed projects</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="dark">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white">When scope is clear, building gets easier.</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <Button href="/contact" size="lg">Get a quote</Button>
        <Button href="/work" size="lg" variant="secondary">View work</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>